title: Introduction to React
description: Begin your React journey by understanding its core features.
content: This lesson covers the basics of React, including JSX, components, and the importance of state management.
video_transcript: Transcript of the video covering React's core concepts.

title: Svelte Basics
description: An overview of Svelte and its unique approach to front-end development.
content: Learn about Svelte's innovative approach to building user interfaces, with a focus on its reactive update model.

title: Getting Started with Vue
description: An introductory lesson on setting up and understanding the basics of Vue.js.
content: Learn how to set up Vue.js and explore its fundamental concepts. Understand Vue's template syntax, reactivity system, and component basics.
video_transcript: Transcript of the video covering Vue.js setup and basics.

title: Introduction to Astro
description: Get acquainted with Astro and its approach to building faster websites.
content: This lesson introduces Astro's capabilities in static site generation and its component-based architecture.
video_transcript: Transcript of the video explaining Astro's features and benefits.

title: Vue Components and Reactivity
description: Dive deeper into Vue components and the reactivity system.
content: Explore how Vue components work and how Vue's reactivity system makes your apps dynamic and responsive.
